{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/space-drop-en-Compete-for-Galactic-Glory.png?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The year is 2142, and New Earth is buzzing with excitement as the prestigious Universe Space Jumper Championship begins. You, a rookie competitor, must face off against the galaxy\u2019s most skilled Space Jumpers. With high stakes and the weight of the universe on your shoulders, you must jump through warp tunnels to prove yourself, earn your glory, and become a symbol of hope for humanity\u2019s future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/Start320.gif?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/space-drop-en-Leap-Into-Thrilling-Warp-Tunnels.png?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the fast-paced action of Space Drop. Each level presents an adrenaline-pumping sequence in which you fly through warp tunnels while dodging obstacles, collecting power-ups, shooting down asteroids, and much more. With a vast variety of levels to conquer, each with its own difficulty - every jump becomes a true test of your skill and reflexes. Perfect for those craving fun, fast-paced VR action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/Gameplay320.gif?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/space-drop-en-Survive-With-Power-Ups.png?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Power-ups are key to your survival in Space Drop. Get more shields to recover after hitting obstacles, grab an invincibility pickup for those critical last-second moments, snatch some energy for more ammunition, and gravitate to the nearest points pickup for more score. Learning how to use these power-ups effectively is essential to dominate the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/Pickups320.gif?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/space-drop-en-Create-Your-Own-Levels.png?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience endless replayability with our custom level generator. Tweak a variety of different settings to create your own unique warp tunnels filled with exciting challenges to overcome. Whether you want to create easier levels to slow down the pace, or test your limits with even harder ones - the choice is entirely yours to make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/Generator320.gif?t=1732891632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/space-drop-en-Key-Features.png?t=1732891632\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Leap from spaceships into warp tunnels in VR</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Fly through space at breakneck speeds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Shoot your way through obstacles with your blasters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Collect pickups to adapt your playstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Customize levels with our expansive level generator</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Earn score to top the leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Experience a unique soundtrack as you soar through space</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Easy Rider","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/b1f00d9c97d29f8b3409269b8857ec22c9b80c8e.jpg"},{"name":"Medium Fried","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/65a2e968ceb92c8558847ecdd5b4d5bcce13f519.jpg"},{"name":"Hard Life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/8a63beb7d76626b6d2b9fc147ac8f430cab7a880.jpg"},{"name":"Evaded","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/72995059231affee174f1e23bab12f3dd88c7771.jpg"},{"name":"Asteroid Killer Bronze","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/5a82a0e7e3f5bc31035c51a5c232e016bb3a130d.jpg"},{"name":"Asteroid Killer Silver","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/453e1c4b92e4bbc3cc1fc8983c61d1771f52e9c0.jpg"},{"name":"Asteroid Killer Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/563f45bb5a47c1e4bbc0e4aeaa118a066093e41c.jpg"},{"name":"Squirrel Bronze","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/e3eddbfb8a6a2b6d1708ffe7add578fd3d24b5e5.jpg"},{"name":"Squirrel Silver","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/04363b7c2a3d769cf9fbf17bb549c5601f87725a.jpg"},{"name":"Squirrel Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2605140/f6e92be878edd4a10e41202b6a8f2588281c6f5b.jpg"}],"total":10},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2605140?t=173289163